videos.description: Dorian Pickens grabs a loose ball and makes an acrobatic layup through multiple defenders in transition early against Stanford.
videos.headline: Pickens weaves through defense on the fast break

videos.description: Romello White blocks a shot at the rim, tosses an outlet to Kodi Justice who finishes with a one-handed flush.
videos.headline: Sun Devils turn defense into offense

videos.description: Josh Sharma swats away Tra Holder's layup with authority late in the first half.
videos.headline: Sharma spikes Holder's layup attempt into the crowd

videos.description: Josh Sharma rocks the rim after a couple quick and accurate passes in the paint by Stanford.
videos.headline: Great ball movement sets up Sharma slam

videos.description: Josh Sharma swats away a layup on one end then smashes down a posterizing dunk on the other end.
videos.headline: Sharma owns the rim on both ends of the floor

videos.description: Josh Sharma continues to own the rim after flying through the lane for monstrous putback dunk.
videos.headline: Sharma gets the crowd on their feet with putback slam
